  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "9 new features. 73 bug fixes. 14 improvements.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3c9983d895319916e8bed2f6def1f49be1bd2c0fb17eb5188c7648fb87124a23",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "The biggest shifts land on agent management, goal-driven runs, and auto-mode safety.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a493e62c245b22bc6a53b4fde68dd82ea2fc4fe1cb7bb4843e03bba9bce73025",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 4.73687074829932,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 8
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "First. The new agents view lists every Claude Code session you have.",
      "checksum": "sha256:051405901c2904ebd87b8ef40d8701c85d4d5834f1b851dcf7740ea955532ab3",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 4.179591836734694,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 20
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Running, blocked, or done. Run claude agents to see them all in one place.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c883d06799b0b7b3e559ce63829a5ded97235c5e9dbb52c95a1b8e69a1582800",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 4.783310657596372,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 32
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Second. The slash goal command sets a completion condition.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ea427b5ac8a93a42964acbc134b340bf7388f7d7f930f0cd8f7da0a0e268c51a",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 46
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Claude keeps working across turns until it is met.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e0439f5dcbe541bd7fc296010c7ac12d0f11a2ff528978dcaedc61a6c09abe50",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 55
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Elapsed time, turn count, and tokens update as it runs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5d19a6296ac74bcb41ba96064eef4e24f1679fd7bf8a6c2d1f031aa0153bc623",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 3.3436734693877552,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 64
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Third. The settings dot auto mode dot hard deny rule blocks actions unconditionally.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9556cb3ee3c012ea922a49ba1ec978c212948e89ad7e376a7715097073fbbdda",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 5.433469387755102,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 74
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "The classifier can no longer override it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:db0255c9461f5807d9783f77efbc39c7d3519a3e5777f7a9b682f6dae07a1729",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 2.2755555555555556,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 87
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "The absolute no you have been waiting for.",
      "checksum": "sha256:81e11f714d368f8245321b4248888a349008b1c4713d1ac297b72c6559f647f7",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 94
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Fourth. Transcript view finally has keyboard navigation.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1dbcffabf6bec240efb10afa44701f4b6c3c73dbfefeb28208d6170ecfca7220",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 102
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Question mark for shortcuts, curly braces to jump between user prompts, and v to toggle the panel.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e275a799d6ba335d3da1e2740d4235ac6e68c21f86d84d17725042ed2353f45e",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 5.61922902494331,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 109
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Fifth. Claude plugin details shows a plugin's components and its projected token cost.",
      "checksum": "sha256:638f4d9d3a80a84c1175ba5abdb2dd12fc5719e78c9c8d1063623603328f9ff8",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 5.154829931972789,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 126
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "The price tag before you install. Sixth.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2a8d29dc9acab5869c19cfb6d563639a53472f6476f78ea211e7e48d7518223c",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 141
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Multi server M C P setups no longer lose O auth tokens during concurrent refreshes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0291cfc52ef10842c6b93cbed2e077e4789142006e65956b3108b21a3733cab1",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 148
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "The daily re auth dance is over. Seventh.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3db8f751c1510e6230b5fdaffac0e7f091fa5ebcf8abde229bc7e28591ea19d2",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 163
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "The compaction prompt now asks the model to preserve your instructions.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e5fb16ad652c9df1bac03a672426eaffe9a2731c511d30c7c532c53b5649edc5",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 3.7151927437641725,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 171
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Long sessions no longer lose user intent when context gets trimmed.\n\nEighth.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dc3a6bdb436265452f2386794574ed2e386d7da8ba51101d840a0ff03ad47496",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 4.179591836734694,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 182
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "The deadlock that blocked claude auth login, logout, and status is patched. Expired credentials no longer hang the entire C L I.",
      "checksum": "sha256:af81a4809270fa54c2299a17f57c7631b72d47de94f180418e8ff3a979a2e03d",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 7.383945578231293,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 194
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Ninth. Slash M C P reconnect now picks up dot mcp dot json edits live.",
      "checksum": "sha256:29e95b9ea5e8502be00867e675704ab09b918996d9d563e2a2fb78850acd48a4",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 5.526349206349207,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 216
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "No restart needed when you tweak server config.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ee046a1979add38a7f3b41ba1987a53c86f38c439d269a45a1ad827326dd3d05",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 2.461315192743764,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 231
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "Which patch matters most. Agent view. Slash goal.",
      "checksum": "sha256:eee9e78e107b0da8db01e9fd6d6b430a4fba0dea27f37cc59825035f05b3d386",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 239
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Or hard deny. Drop a comment. If you want to learn more about AI, check out the dynamous dot ai community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:41de92ee9a61c04f7ee950f14f0c48a94e9b2b0c923b8d512b17838c2f99fb5c",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 7.662585034013605,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 247
    }
  ]
}